txt.en: 'We cannot rest with simply taking this tower. We must defend it. So get your scrawny arse out into the wild and get the materials we need to build a gate to keep the Free People out of the tower!'
Deliver the materials to Gaath at Tiríth Rhaw
'Well, well, seems we do have some maggots what is good at taking orders. You shall avoid the lash for this effort. But, don't think that this makes you anything more than a maggot, maggot.\q
You are ordered to acquire materials needed to build a gate that will defend the exterior of Tiriíth Rhaw.
Defence: Build a Gate at Tiríth Rhaw
'Do you want the tyrant to lash you to the walls? Get out there and do as I command!'
Make your way into the wilds of the Ettenmoors and collect the materials needed to construct the external gate.
